<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TCV98">
<l>maṟantuṟantu vañcamāṟṟi yaimpulaṉka ḷācaiyun</l>
<l>tuṟantuniṉka ṇācaiyēto ṭarntuniṉṟa nāyiṉēṉ</l>
<l>piṟantiṟantu pēriṭarccu ḻikkaṇiṉṟu nīṅkumā</l>
<l>maṟantiṭātu maṟṟeṉakku māyanalka veṇṭumē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Without forgetting, [You] should bestow upon me the means for me, a dog—</l>
<l>whose desire for you has increased, renouncing anger, dispelling deceit,</l>
<l>renouncing the desires of the five sense organs—to be released from the eddy</l>
<l>that is the great calamity of being born and dying, and further! O wonderful [Lord]!</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
